""" Run 'git up' with result: (fast) fast-forwarding """
os.chdir(repo_path)
assert_not_equal(master.branches[test_name].commit, repo.branches[test_name
    ].commit)
assert_not_equal(master.branches[test_name].commit, repo.branches[test_name +
    '.2'].commit)
from PyGitUp.gitup import GitUp
gitup = GitUp(testing=True)
gitup.run()
assert_equal(len(gitup.states), 2)
assert_equal(gitup.states[0], 'fast-forwarding')
assert_equal(gitup.states[1], 'fast-forwarding')
assert_equal(master.branches[test_name].commit, repo.branches[test_name].commit
    )
assert_equal(master.branches[test_name].commit, repo.branches[test_name +
    '.2'].commit)
